    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The assessment team reviewed available simulation and experimental evidence for the VAD hemolysis CFD model and determined that the overall body of evidence is sufficient to support regulatory submission. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was completed and results are within acceptable bounds for the primary operating envelope. The team notes that several factors were not formally leveled but considers the qualitative evidence adequate given the conservative safety margins applied to the hemolysis threshold. No structured reconciliation of factor-level gaps against the Accepted outcome was performed.",
